refront-to-Cloud Distributed Architecture Diagram*, and a *Zero-Trust Customer Privacy Guardrail Demo*. Finally, for *TelecomVerse Core*, I'm building an *Interactive Network Topology & Optical Carrier Load Router*.\n\n\n**Implementing Premium Features**\n\nI'm now focused on implementing premium features with a unique design language for each page. Specifically, for *TelecomVerse Core*, I am designing interactive SVGs to showcase carrier-grade optical transport, fiber cut simulations, and GFF agent routing. I'm exploring a carrier-grade uptime timeline or a sovereign sandbox boundary demo, all with a dark background and red/blue accents. I'm moving beyond generic SaaS design elements.\n\n\n"}}
