className=\"text-white/70 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed\">\n              Managing distributed retail environments requires low latency and high availability. RetailMesh consolidates transaction logs, active store inventories, and associate search logs, routing query patterns to context-aware retail agents instantly.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </MotionReveal>\n\n        <MotionReveal className=\"space-y-6\">\n          <h2 className=\"text-xl font-bold text-white text-center\">Interactive Storefront Simulator</h2>\n          <div className=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#04060b] overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:flex-row\">\n            <div className=\"flex-grow p-6 bg-black/40 border-r border-white/5 flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[160px] relative\">\n              <span className=\"absolute top-3 left-3 text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 tracking-widest uppercase\">RetailMesh Location Map</span>\n              <div className=\"flex gap-4 mt-6\">\n                {[\"store-104\", \"store-209\", \"store-312\"].map((s) => (\n                  <button\n                    key={s} onClick={() => runSim(s, tab)}\n                    className={`p-3 rounded-lg border text-xs capitalize transition-all ${store === s ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5 text-[#009DFF]\" : \"border-white/5 bg-black text-white/60\"}`}\n                  >\n                    <ShoppingBag className=\"w-4 h-4 mx-auto mb-1 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n                    {s.replace(\"-\", \" \")}\n                  </button>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"w-full md:w-[280px] p-5 flex flex-col justify-between bg-black/20 text-xs\">\n              <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase tracking-wider block\">Simulator Mode</span>\n                <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n                  <button onClick={() => { setTab(\"pos\"); runSim(store, \"pos\"); }} className={`px-2.5 py-1 text-xs border rounded ${tab === \"pos\" ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5 text-white\" : \"border-white/5 text-white/50\"}`}>POS Streams</button>\n                  <button onClick={() => { setTab(\"support\"); runSim(store, \"support\"); }} className={`px-2.5 py-1 text-xs border rounded ${tab === \"support\" ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5 text-white\" : \"border-white/5 text-white/50\"}`}>Support</button>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-white/5\">\n                <pre className=\"p-2.5 rounded bg-black text-[10px] font-mono text-emerald-400 border border-white/5 h-[80px] overflow-y-auto whitespace-pre-wrap\">{log}</pre>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </MotionReveal>\n\n        <Carousel items={MODULES} />\n\n        <BentoGrid className=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\">\n          <BentoCard title=\"PCI-DSS Compliant\" description=\"Automatic masking of buyer identity, credit details, and loyalty tokens.\" badge=\"Security\" icon={<Shield className=\"w-5 h-5\" />} />\n          <BentoCard title=\"99.99% Store Uptime\" description=\"Hybrid edge replication preserves transaction flows during connection drops.\" badge=\"Reliability\" icon={<Zap className=\"w-5 h-5\" />} />\n          <BentoCard title=\"Real-time Analytics\" description=\"Enables direct merchandiser dashboards to visualize sales trends.\" badge=\"Latency\" icon={<Activity className=\"w-5 h-5\" />} />\n        </BentoGrid>\n\n        <RelatedPagesGrid links={[\n          { title: \"Retail Solutions\", tag: \"Industry Core\", desc: \"Discover how GFF's multi-agent architectures optimize retail chains.\", href: \"/industries/retail\" },\n          { title: \"Control Center\", tag: \"Cockpit Console\", desc: \"Monitor edge swarm health, compute spend, and rule audit logs.\", href: \"/platforms/control-center\" }\n        ]} />\n\n        <PremiumCTA\n          title=\"Optimize Your Multi-Store Enterprise Flow\"\n          description=\"Schedule a technical workspace audit with GFF retail systems leads to connect your registers securely.\"\n          primaryLabel=\"Connect with GFF AI\"\n          primaryHref=\"/contact\"\n        />\n      </div>\n    </InnerPageShell>\n  );\n}","new_text":"  return (\n    <InnerPageShell>\n      {/* SECTION 1: HERO */}\n      <InnerPageHero\n        category=\"Omnichannel Mesh • Secure Visibility\"\n        title=\"RetailMesh Platform\"\n        highlightedWord=\"RetailMesh\"\n        description=\"A secure retail mesh unifying point-of-sale telemetry, inventory visibility, and real-time associate support across thousands of physical storefronts and digital hubs.\"\n        breadcrumbs={[{ label: \"Platforms\", href: \"/platforms\" }, { label: \"RetailMesh\" }]}\n      />\n\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24 space-y-24\">\n        {/* SECTION 2: STATEMENT */}\n        <div id=\"retailmesh-statement\" />\n\n        {/* SECTION 3: TOPOLOGY */}\n        <div id=\"retailmesh-topology\" />\n\n        {/* SECTION 4: SIMULATOR */}\n        <div id=\"retailmesh-simulator\" />\n\n        {/* SECTION 5: CAROUSEL */}\n        <div id=\"retailmesh-carousel\" />\n\n        {/* SECTION 6: BENTO */}\n        <div id=\"retailmesh-bento\" />\n\n        {/* SECTION 7: RELATED */}\n        <RelatedPagesGrid links={[\n          { title: \"Retail Solutions\", tag: \"Industry Core\", desc: \"Discover how GFF's multi-agent architectures optimize retail chains.\", href: \"/industries/retail\" },\n          { title: \"Control Center\", tag: \"Cockpit Console\", desc: \"Monitor edge swarm health, compute spend, and rule audit logs.\", href: \"/platforms/control-center\" }\n        ]} />\n\n        {/* SECTION 8: CTA */}\n        <PremiumCTA\n          title=\"Optimize Your Multi-Store Enterprise Flow\"\n          description=\"Schedule a technical workspace audit with GFF retail systems leads to connect your registers and inventory secure.\"\n          primaryLabel=\"Connect with GFF AI\"\n          primaryHref=\"/contact\"\n        />\n      </div>\n    </InnerPageShell>\n  );\n}"}}}
